[color=#00ff00]SKYTEMPLE[/color] a Players home.

[color=#00ff00]
Entrance[/color] to [color=#00ff00]SKYTEMPLE[/color] see picture for info.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[color=#e69138]Requirements: [/color]Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.


[color=#e69138]Installation:[/color] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,              
                   then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[color=#e69138]
Unistallation: [/color] Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.

[color=#00ff00][size=4]CREDITS:[/size] Many thanks to     "Malo Statues by Malo" 
                                         
                                               "cad435 for Snow Elves Remastered" 

                                               "Varlaisaran for his Adabala Building System - Ayleid Transfusion"   [/color]                      

 Cleaned with TES5Edit.         


I hope you enjoy the home.

My Regards to you all.

Thank You. 


I am at the moment building another home mod, this will be my last one, i have given homes i hoped most players enjoy but i feel the endorse button was amiss by most players, so i can only assume my work on the home mods did not hit the spot for most players,so many many thanks to all players that did enjoy my mods and endorsed them.



Thank You.
